<%= content_for :page_title, 'Home' %>

<section class="hero">
	<div class="content">
		<h1 class="xl">
			Leveraging open civic data and collaboration to make Greensboro, NC even better.
		</h1>
		<h4 class="brighten">Coming soon: <%=link_to "Civic Hackathon", "http://hackathon.codeforgreensboro.org", :class => "special_snowflake" %></h4>
	</div>
</section>

<div class="content">
	<h3 class="is-centered">
		Code for Greensboro works to improve the way our city government uses its data and the web. And we need you&mdash;no coding required.
	</h3>
</div>

<%= @events %>

<section class="top-deck">
	<div class="content">
		<div class="panel two-up">
			<h4 class="blue">What We Do</h4>
			<p>
				Code for America Brigades are volunteer groups that collaborate with local government and community partners to build new tools that help with local civic issues. Code for America supports Brigade chapters with resources, tools, and access to the wider civic technology movement.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="panel two-up">
			<h4 class="blue">Who We Are</h4>
			<p>
				We are developers, designers, data nerds, politically-minded people with ideas for making things better, citizens, users of software&mdash;in other words, we are this community. We want to use these talents to make government work with the web in new and better ways.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="calls">
	<div class="content">

		<div class="panel four-up">
			<h4>September 16, 2015</h4>
			<p>Join us at HQ Greensboro, 111 W Lewis Street in Downtown Greensboro.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="panel four-up">
			<h4>Attend A Meeting</h4>
			<p>We meet on first and third Wednesdays from 6:30 PM-9:00 PM. RSVP <%=link_to "here", "http://bit.ly/cfgrsvp" %>.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="panel four-up">
			<h4>Slack With Us</h4>
			<p>Join the Code for Greensboro <%=link_to "Slack channel", "http://slack.codeforgreensboro.org" %> to talk to us about ideas or say hello.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="panel four-up">
			<h4>Meetup Group</h4>
			<p><%=link_to "Join our Meetup group", "http://www.meetup.com/Code-for-Greensboro" %> to be notified of new events and happenings.</p>
		</div>

	</div>
</section>
